graph TD
    A[Raw Text Input] --> B[setup_logging]
    B --> C[Initialize Components]
    C --> D[split_into_chunks]
    D --> E{For each chunk}
    E --> F[regex_filter]
    F --> G{Passed filter?}
    G -->|No| H[Log & Skip]
    G -->|Yes| I[llm_classifier.classify]
    I --> J{Relevant + High Confidence?}
    J -->|Yes| K[Add to Results]
    J -->|No/Uncertain| L[Log for Review]
    K --> M[Next Chunk]
    L --> M
    H --> M
    M --> E
    E -->|All done| N[Return Results]